177 A.3d 131 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. LORETTA C. BURROUGHS, A/K/A LORETTA D. DOYLE, LORETTA DOYLD, LORETTA THOMAS, LORETTA C. TOKASH, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-455 September Term 2017

079755 December 13, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004590-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
